## Why Multi-language Support Matters

In today's interconnected world, having software that speaks your language is no longer a luxury but a necessity. By introducing multi-language support, undb offers:

* Better User Experience: Work in the language you're most comfortable with.
* Global Collaboration: Teams from different regions can collaborate effortlessly on the same platform.
* Accessibility: Lower barriers for users who aren't fluent in English, empowering them to harness the full potential of undb.

